  "description.machine_max.blueprint.ae86": "The AE86 is a compact, lightweight, economy-oriented car produced by Toyota, introduced in 1983 as the fourth-generation Corolla. Toyota's launch of the TERCEL in 1978 marked the beginning of a shift in small cars from the simple but costly and space-consuming FR (front-engine, rear-wheel drive) layout to the more complex but cost-effective FF (front-engine, front-wheel drive) layout, driven by advances in automotive technology.",
  "description.machine_max.blueprint.ae86at": "This AE86 has been modified with a four-wheel drive system, a more powerful engine, a compatible transmission, and all-terrain tires, greatly enhancing its off-road capability.",
  "description.machine_max.blueprint.mini_ev": "The Hongguang miniEV is the first four-seat new energy vehicle under the Wuling brand of SAIC-GM-Wuling, officially launched on July 24, 2020. It focuses on short-distance convenient travel scenarios, striving to become the 'people's mobility scooter'.",
  "description.machine_max.blueprint.jeep": "The Jeep Wrangler is a classic off-road vehicle from the Jeep brand, known for its powerful off-road performance and rugged body structure, suitable for driving in various complex terrains.",
  "description.machine_max.blueprint.dayun": "The Dayun Heavy Truck is a heavy-duty truck produced by China's Dayun Automobile, featuring strong load capacity and reliable performance, widely used in logistics transportation and construction projects.",
  "description.machine_max.blueprint.wine_fox": "The Wine Fox Car is a uniquely designed small urban commuter vehicle with a fashionable and cute appearance, suitable for short-distance travel in cities.",
  "description.machine_max.blueprint.wine_fox_gt": "The Wine Fox Car is a uniquely designed small urban commuter vehicle with a fashionable and cute appearance, with a better performance after upgrading.",
  "description.machine_max.blueprint.kluo": "KLUO Car is a classic-style compact oil-to-electric sedan. Despite its limited range, its acceleration capability and top speed should not be underestimated.",
  "description.machine_max.blueprint.kluo_gt": "KLUO Car is a classic-style compact oil-to-electric sedan. With the GT upgrade package, handling and track capability are further improved.",
  "description.machine_max.blueprint.r700": "The Pathfinder R700 is a multi-functional off-road vehicle designed specifically for exploration and outdoor activities, featuring good passability and reliability.",
  "description.machine_max.blueprint.senna_gtr": "The McLaren Senna GTR is an extreme track-focused supercar featuring advanced aerodynamic design, including a large rear wing, diffuser, and front splitter. These elements generate enormous downforce at high speeds, ensuring exceptional stability and handling. Its lightweight construction and powerful powertrain make it a true king on the racetrack.",
  "description.machine_max.blueprint.van": "This van may be inexpensive, but with outstanding reliability and practicality, it has become a loyal partner for countless families starting small businesses. It does not chase looks, only capacity. Its battle-tested chassis and powertrain keep moving forward under heavy loads in both cities and rural roads. This humble van has carried building materials, freight, and hope, helping many ordinary people earn their first bucket of gold. It is not a race car, but in the hearts of strivers, it is still the fastest lap toward a better life.",


